<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmed · Frost & Scoop</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Your premium ice cream order has been received. Thank you for choosing Frost & Scoop.">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #0d0b0a;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      line-height: 1.5;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    h1, .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }

    .container { max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }

    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 999;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(13, 11, 10, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e8e0d8; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .logo i { color: #d4af37; margin-right: 6px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.2rem; font-weight: 500; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #c8c0b8;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { border-bottom-color: #d4af37; color: #d4af37; }

    .success-hero {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0d0b0a 0%, #1a1512 100%);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .success-hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 40%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 60%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .success-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 600px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      color: #d4af37;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      animation: pulseCheck 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulseCheck {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .success-content h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e8e0d8;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .success-content h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #f0d060, #d4af37);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: goldShine 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes goldShine { 0%,100%{background-position:0% 50%;} 50%{background-position:100% 50%;} }
    .success-content p {
      color: #a89888;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .success-content .order-ref {
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06);
      border-radius: 1.2rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
      color: #8a7a6a;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.9rem 2.8rem;
      border-radius: 60px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #b8941e);
      color: #0d0b0a;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px -8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    }
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px -8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0c040, #d4af37);
    }
    .btn i { margin-right: 0.5rem; }

    footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .footer-links a { margin: 0 1rem 0 0; color: #8a7a6a; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s ease; font-weight: 300; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: #d4af37; }
    .footer-links span { color: #4a3a2a; }
    .social i { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-left: 1rem; color: #5a4a3a; transition: 0.3s ease; }
    .social i:hover { color: #d4af37; transform: scale(1.1); }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .nav-links { gap: 1rem; }
      .container { padding: 0 1.2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="logo"><i class="fas fa-ice-cream"></i> Frost & Scoop</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="menu-ice-cream-shop.html">Menu</a></li>
    <li><a href="contactus-ice-cream-shop.html">Contact</a></li>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="success-hero">
  <div class="success-content">
    <div class="success-icon"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></div>
    <h1>Order <span>Confirmed!</span></h1>
    <p>Thank you for choosing Frost & Scoop. Your premium ice cream order has been received and we're getting it ready for you.</p>
    <div class="order-ref"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Order #FS-<span id="orderRef">2026-001</span></div>
    <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#6a5a4a;">You'll receive a confirmation at your email shortly. We'll notify you when your order is on its way.</p>
    <a href="index.html" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Return Home</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="container">
  <div class="footer-links">
    <a href="index.html">Home</a> <a href="menu-ice-cream-shop.html">Menu</a> <a href="contactus-ice-cream-shop.html">Contact</a> <span>© 2026 Frost & Scoop</span>
  </div>
  <div class="social">
    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
    <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
    <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  // Generate a simple random order reference
  document.getElementById('orderRef').textContent = 
    'FS-' + String(Math.floor(1000 + Math.random() * 9000));
</script>

</body>
</html>
